maven-shared-io (3.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Team upload.
  * New upstream release
    - Depend on libmaven3-core-java instead of libmaven2-core-java
    - Depend on libwagon2-java instead of libwagon-java
    - Removed the patches (fixed usptream)
    - New build dependency on junit4
  * debian/control:
    - Use canonical URLs for the Vcs-* fields
    - Standards-Version updated to 4.0.0 (no changes)
  * Build with the DH sequencer instead of CDBS
  * Switch to debhelper level 10
  * debian/copyright: Updated the Format URI
  * Moved the package to Git
  * Use XZ compression for the upstream tarball

 -- Emmanuel Bourg <ebourg@apache.org>  Wed, 19 Jul 2017 19:16:56 +0200

